{"tid":685453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平案揭涉事者黑客身份","createTime":"2018-05-31T12:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T00:14:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"415ec11567bbc760ae83a31fcc842e5633dd5a68","tid":685453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180531/20406589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180531%2F20406589&d=Ak3NfAWZMzwFovJ%2BXfxSZCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e03d60ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180531%2F20406589&h=e3e15d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180531/20406589</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月31日 <br />\n<br />\n何志平案揭涉事者黑客身份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180531/large/31la7p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180531%2Flarge%2F31la7p12.jpg&h=5bfb5031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何志平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港美政府均無公開被拒引渡疑犯身份，但原來早前美國審理前民政事務局局長何志平涉貪案時，曾披露一名在港被捕的澳門黑客，聯同兩名中國人涉入侵美國律師行電腦，盜取資料再投資股票，獲利至少400萬美元，疑犯其後在港被捕，但港府卻拒絕引渡，亦成為美方反對何保釋的理據。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑入侵美律師行<br />\n<br />\n前民政事務局局長何志平涉貪，去年在美國被捕，辯方律師爭取保釋時，曾引用Iat Hong案做例，指港美設有具效力的引渡協議。不過，檢控官今年2月向法官致函反駁辯方，首次披露港府拒絕Hong的引渡申請，時間與美國國務院報告提及的案件脗合，檢控官更相信Hong永遠也不會被引渡。最終法官同意引渡協議未必有效，加上其他因素，至今拒絕何保釋。<br />\n<br />\n該宗案件指2016年12月，美國司法部檢控三名中國公民，指他們涉盜取兩間美國律師行的機密資料，再投資股票，獲利逾400萬美元。疑犯分別是約27歲的澳門居民Iat Hong、約51歲澳門居民Chin Hung及約31歲中國長沙居民Bo Zheng。<br />\n<br />\n其中Hong在2016年12月25日於香港被捕，美國司法部當時表示，Hong即將面臨引渡程序，他亦已在香港法庭過堂，不過其後未有引渡至美國。<br />\n<br />\n港美政府於1996年12月簽訂引渡協議，但設有不少豁免條款，如涉及的案件是關於國防、外交或重要的中國公眾利益或政策，港府都可拒絕引渡任何中國公民。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳建平  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美設《香港政策法》區別中港<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n紅van撞壆翻側　司機受傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美設《香港政策法》區別中港<br />\n<br />\n港拒向美移交逃犯　衝擊一國兩制中方不滿美說三道四"},{"pid":"06e99d8908bc1349fac1bebe7efd569d3baa30b4","tid":685453,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"制裁鄰國順手制裁埋香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725b8113043b6b728c96c048c51829b3964f830a","tid":685453,"uid":25424,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"英雄安心上路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6dfffa170ba25f5e1d35fa0eb8a0d31e65d3c05","tid":685453,"uid":18722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"因小失大"},{"pid":"da3d4d54cecc84aca342f8715260daa6e1df193e","tid":685453,"uid":30988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:58:45.000Z","msg":"辯方律師引條失敗案例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n擺明國家想俾肥平做英雄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae735e2bcd73f757c4bc79809142dd2ad4538b5d","tid":685453,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"如果777去美國會唔會好似肥仔平咁？"},{"pid":"7a1824203b5521568a2a07b89bdb465123c8f643","tid":685453,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4f31094bf9e43301eba6f6d9d2e6dc547d53bbf6","tid":685453,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"鬼佬唔會再信港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁把炮咪靠共產黨養起八百萬人囉"},{"pid":"e63bf2fe556dee5a79f01a2b14b5a493fe03dac3","tid":685453,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05